imdb.plot outline: Darcy Peregrine hosts Looking Back, a 20-to-1 type show that reminisces over the best that Australian TV has ever offered. The shows reflected on aren't real, but rather scathing and loving parodies of Aussie television. Written and performed by the sharp and unusual comedy trio of Greg Larsen, Henry Stone and Sam Campbell, the debut episode focuses on a prank style show "Dack Attack" and it's alpha male host Darren Tackle.
imdb.title: Looking Back
plot: _Looking Back_ (qv) is the show that remembers some of the greatest moments in Australian TV that never happened.::producer

Darcy Peregrine hosts _Looking Back_ (qv), a 20-to-1 type show that reminisces over the best that Australian TV has ever offered. The shows reflected on aren't real, but rather scathing and loving parodies of Aussie television. Written and performed by the sharp and unusual comedy trio of Greg Larsen, Henry Stone and Sam Campbell, the debut episode focuses on a prank style show "Dack Attack" and it's alpha male host Darren Tackle.::producer
